Package ides.api.core

Interface Summary
Annotable Interface for objects which can be dynamically annotated by other parts of the code.
OptionsPane The interface for modules that will appear in the Options dialog box.
UserInterface Interface for the services provided by the main window interface.
Workspace Interface for the main manager (workspace) of DESModels in IDES.
WorkspaceSubscriber Implemented by classes that wish to receive change notifications from the Workspace.

PersistentProperties A convenience wrapper of Properties.

Exception Summary
